Detailed Description

Description:
: Test the TA cryptographic functions TEE_InitRefAttribute, TEE_SetOperationKey, TEE_CipherInit, TEE_CipherDoFinal

Function Documentation

TestCase_GC00100_KAT_AES_128_ECB_NOPAD (  )
Trusted Applications dependencies:
3519aef478ba57daa6ff7523fc05cfdd
Pre Conditions:
Test files available in test_data/vectors/ directory
Description:
KAT tests for AES-128-ECB-NOPAD. Crypto operation done on single input block of data.
Focus:
TEE_InitRefAttribute, TEE_SetOperationKey, TEE_CipherInit, TEE_CipherUpdate, TEE_CipherDoFinal
Test Steps:
Reads input data and expected from file. Performs encryption or decryption and compares results.
Verification:
TEE_CipherInit, TEE_CipherUpdate, TEE_CipherDoFinal APIs succeed.
